OL,3,CITV's disproportionate Scottish
OL,4,CBorders commitments
OL,6,GIf you live in the Scottish Borders or
OL,7,GDumfries and Galloway are you
OL,8,Gsuperserved by ITV?
OL,10,FThe south of Scotland is a rural area
OL,11,Fwith several medium-sized towns but
OL,12,Fnowhere of real size.
OL,14,FThe largest town, Dumfries, has a
OL,15,Fpopulation of 33,000.
OL,17,FThe area itself can feel overshadowed
OL,18,Fby the densely populated Central Belt
OL,19,Fof Scotland.
