OL,3,CITV's disproportionate Scottish
OL,4,CBorders commitments
OL,6,FAnd local residents may sometimes feel
OL,7,Ftheir interests are not as well served
OL,8,Fas they could be by the Scottish
OL,9,Fnational media.
OL,11,FBBC Scotland, of course, provides a
OL,12,Fnational news service for Scotland on
OL,13,FTV which includes stories from the
OL,14,Fsouth but purely local stories are not
OL,15,Fin the remit of Reporting Scotland.
OL,17,FThe BBC does however provide opt-out
OL,18,Fradio bulletins in the area and plenty
OL,19,Fof stories from there feature on the
OL,20,FBBC website.
