OL,3,CITV's disproportionate Scottish
OL,4,CBorders commitments
OL,6,FCommercial radio though has all but
OL,7,Fdisappeared.
OL,9,FRadio Borders, once one of the most
OL,10,Fsuccessful independent local radio
OL,11,Fstations in Britain and an important
OL,12,Fpart of the local community, was
OL,13,Freplaced by Greatest Hits Radio last
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FSo was Westsound in Dumfries. It is
OL,17,Fthought their remaining local news
OL,18,Fbulletins are compiled and presented
OL,19,Ffrom centralised hubs.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/10
