OL,3,CITV's disproportionate Scottish
OL,4,CBorders commitments
OL,6,FThe area has many well-established
OL,7,Flocal weekly papers but, just as
OL,8,Feverywhere else, they have suffered as
OL,9,Fsales have fallen and advertisers have
OL,10,Fgone online.
OL,12,FSo it is reasonable to argue this is
OL,13,Fan area of the country which can
OL,14,Fsometimes be overlooked by the
OL,15,FScottish national media and where the
OL,16,Flocal media is fragile.
OL,18,FExcept when it comes to ITV. Here the
OL,19,Fvery opposite is true and the company
OL,20,Fcarries an unfair burden.
