OL,3,CITV's disproportionate Scottish
OL,4,CBorders commitments
OL,6,FIn 2013, Ofcom decreed that ITV should
OL,7,Freinstate a full news service for the
OL,8,FBorder TV region which includes
OL,9,FCumbria as well as the south of
OL,10,FScotland. A few years earlier the
OL,11,Fstation was effectively merged with
OL,12,FTyne Tees.
OL,14,FIt also decreed that additional local
OL,15,Fprogrammes would need to be provided
OL,16,Ffor the Scottish part of the region.
OL,18,FTypically 2 hours a week are provided
OL,19,F` a magazine programme Border Life and
OL,20,Fa thrice-weekly political programme
OL,21,FRepresenting Border.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/10
