OL,3,CITV's disproportionate Scottish
OL,4,CBorders commitments
OL,6,FRatings are not publicly available but
OL,7,Fthe viewing figures for Representing
OL,8,FBorder are thought to be modest.
OL,10,FIt is easy to ask the obvious
OL,11,Fquestion: why not simply change the TV
OL,12,Fregions and give the south of Scotland
OL,13,Fto STV?
OL,15,FApparently Ofcom cannot do this.
OL,16,FEither STV and ITV would need to agree
OL,17,Fthis themselves or a new licence for a
OL,18,Frevised "region" covering all of
OL,19,FScotland would need to be awarded from
OL,20,Fscratch.
