OL,3,CITV's disproportionate Scottish
OL,4,CBorders commitments
OL,6,FBut surely that does not mean that a
OL,7,Fbit of sensible cooperation between
OL,8,FSTV and ITV should not be possible?
OL,10,FSTV produces a well-regarded current
OL,11,Faffairs programme called Scotland
OL,12,FTonight, shown 4 times a week.
OL,13,FPolitics is an important part of the
OL,14,Fprogramme but it covers a broader
OL,15,Frange of topics.
OL,17,FOn Monday night, there will be a
OL,18,Fspecial programme devoted to the
OL,19,FScottish Conservative leadership
OL,20,Felection. This will also be shown on
OL,21,FBorder.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/10
