OL,3,CITV's disproportionate Scottish
OL,4,CBorders commitments
OL,6,FSurely this offers a way forward?
OL,8,FITV and STV could work together to
OL,9,Fcoproduce Scotland Tonight and other
OL,10,Fnon-news regional output. These
OL,11,Fprogrammes would be shown on both STV
OL,12,Fand ITV Border.
OL,14,FSeparately the existing news
OL,15,Farrangements on Channel 3 in Scotland
OL,16,F` including Lookaround for Border
OL,17,Fviewers ` should continue.
OL,19,FIt seems ridiculous that a sparsely
OL,20,Fpopulated part of Scotland should get
OL,21,Fa level of local output unseen
OL,22,Fanywhere else.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G8/10
