OL,6,FSTV programmes outside of news cover
OL,7,Fboth the Central Belt and former
OL,8,FGrampian TV region. English regional
OL,9,Foutput apart from the news is
OL,10,Fvirtually dead.
OL,12,FThe Scottish part of the Border region
OL,13,Fis, in effect, given parity with
OL,14,FWales, Northern Ireland and what is in
OL,15,Feffect STV's Scottish national service.
