OL,6,FInstead STV and ITV should cooperate
OL,7,Fso that STV's non-news output can be
OL,8,Fseen by viewers in the whole of
OL,9,FScotland. Obviously the programmes
OL,10,Fwould need to be modified slightly to
OL,11,Ftake account of this. Issues of
OL,12,Fparticular interest to the Border area
OL,13,Fcould be included within Scotland
OL,14,FTonight on merit.
OL,16,FBut the current Border Scotland burden
OL,17,Fseems completely disproportionate to
OL,18,Fthe size of the area.
OL,20,FTime to bang some heads together.
